song.title: Zapped Out
song.info: From the module : [code]i dont see why we need all these silly chip music writers because if you havent already realised.dis is chip music. but it was done on noisetracker. its called mts. the multi tone system. it was designed and finished by 4-mat of anarchy look out for a new mts-tracker coming soon. music:4-mat[/code] Thanks [user]lroy[/user] for sharing your love with the "old ladies" !
